attributes.title: Cult Camp
attributes.caption: Gwen puts out an ad looking for a new camp counselor, but is not happy with the results. Max suspects there is something off about the new hire.
attributes.description: Gwen puts out an ad looking for a new camp counselor, but is not happy with the results. Max suspects there is something off about the new hire.

attributes.title: Anti-Social Network
attributes.caption: Desperate to get some alone time with his computer, Neil makes a chatbot to distract the other campers. Things seems to be going smoothly until Nikki gets a little too attached...

attributes.title: Quest to Sleepy Peak Peak
attributes.caption: Nerris and Harrison pursue a date with destiny atop an active volcano. Which magic kid will save the day and vanquish the dark forces?

attributes.title: Jermy Fartz
attributes.caption: After making a misguided bet with the Wood Scouts, everyone at Camp Campbell is forced to be nice for a whole day. If that wasn't difficult enough, a new camper has just shown up and he's... a mess.

attributes.title: Jasper Dies at the End
attributes.caption: David reminisces a tale from his younger days back when he was a Campbell camper. When his fellow camper Jasper gets lost on a trek, it's up to young Davey to rescue him. Can he get to him before he's lost forever?

attributes.title: Quartermaster Appreciation Day
attributes.caption: After deciding Quartermaster deserves a day of appreciation, David reunites him with his quarter-sister, a distant relative who is not happy to see him.

attributes.title: Bonjour Bonquisha
attributes.caption: The campers try to help David with his relationship problems. Then the Flower Scouts try to help the campers help David with his relationship problems.

attributes.title: Gwen Gets a Job
attributes.caption: After Max discovers Gwen has been looking for a new job, he blackmails her into finding an elusive treasure. Gwen, desperate to not have David find out, is forced to play along.
attributes.description: After Max discovers Gwen has been looking for a new job, he blackmails her into finding an elusive treasure. Gwen, desperate to not have David find out, is forced to play along.

attributes.title: Eggs Benefits
attributes.caption: The campers are tasked with taking care of some valuable platypus eggs but get so caught up in being parental figures that things start to go awry.
attributes.description: The campers are tasked with taking care of some valuable platypus eggs but get so caught up in being parental figures that things start to go awry.

attributes.title: Space Camp Was a Hoax
attributes.caption: Space Kid is being more spacey than usual, and it's really annoying Max, Neil, and Nikki. Meanwhile, due to a legal loophole, David and Gwen are tasked with faking a moon landing for the would-be astronaut.

attributes.title: Cookin' Cookies
attributes.caption: The Flower Scouts' cookie sale is not going well, and if the girls are gonna win an all-expense paid trip to Cabo, they're gonna have to do some actual work. Ugh, the worst. So they try spicing up their cookies with a secret ingredient!

attributes.title: Parents' Day
attributes.caption: In the season 2 finale, David invites the parents of the campers to come visit. To Campbell's dismay, the future of the camp now hinges on everything going smoothly.

attributes.title: Halloween Special - NIGHT OF THE LIVING ILL
attributes.caption: An epidemic of illness is spreading throughout the camp, causing its victims to turn into snot-nosed zombies. It's up to the few kids spared to find a cure!
